unittitle_ssm: William Thompson Dewart collection of Frank A. Munsey and New York Sun papers
abstract_ssm: A collection of materials relating to newspaper and magazine publisher Frank Munsey, his general manager William T. Dewart, and their publishing and business activities, especially their work on the New York Sun, purchased by Munsey in 1912.  Includes correspondence, photographs, early issues of theSun and other early New York newspapers, and a complete run of theSun Rays, an in-house newspaper produced by theSun's staff.
